text: Diāna Marcinkēviča and Daniela Seguel were the defending champions, but Seguel chose not to participate. Marcinkēviča partnered alongside Alexandra Cadanțu, but lost in the final to Cristina Bucșa and María Fernanda Herazo, 4–6, 6–1, [10–8]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== *Main Draw L'Open 35 de Saint-Malo – Doubles Category:L'Open Emeraude Solaire de Saint-Malo Category:L'Open 35 de Saint-Malo
